Docker/volumes
- Backup volume to prevent data loss.
  https://stackoverflow.com/questions/26331651/how-can-i-backup-a-docker-container-with-its-data-volumes
  Use PZ script in cronjob
  - Stop container
  - Create eco-backup folder in home dir if not existing
  - Create folder based on day date and time
  - Copy files from container to this folder
  - Create tar
  - Remove the folder with day date
  - Clean old backup (keep last 7 days only)
  - Start container

